==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A sudden forward movement, especially with a sword.
# A rope-like piece of tack, more commonly refered to as a [[lunge line]], that is attached to the [[bridle]], [[lungeing cavesson]], or [[halter]] of a horse and is used to control the animal while lungeing.

===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-other-e|lung|e}}

# To make a sudden forward movement.
# To work a horse in a circle around a handler.

